Led by the reluctant hero Captain Zoom, the team searches for young recruits who might save the world—or at least survive training camp! 😄Watch as each kid reveals their quirky and sometimes unpredictable powers. Some impress, some cause a few laughs (and minor explosions), but all of them have something special.
